These are Puzzles for 4x5 Level 1

.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-1::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: game, oliveros, havana, montecristo, chaman
The people prefer 5 different music-genres: hip-hop, indie, ambient, gospel, metal
There are 5 different favourite colors: turquise, red, yellow, amber, grey
The people have 5 different jobs:  designer, writer, manager, fisherman, nurse
 1. the manager is on the left of the person who likes grey##1
 2. the nurse is the chaman-smoker##1
 3. the writer is on the right of the fan of hip-hop##1
 4. the designer is on the right of the fan of ambient##1
 5. the person who likes red is the fan of gospel##1
 6. the fan of indie is the oliveros-smoker##1
 7. the person who likes turquise is on the left of the fisherman##1
 8. the fan of indie is on the far left##1
 9. the game-smoker is on the right of the fan of indie##1
10. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the designer##1
11. the person who likes red is the designer##1
12. the person who likes yellow is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2     |    3    |     4     |    5     |
| Cigar         | oliveros  | game    | montecristo | havana    | chaman  |
| Music-Genre   | indie  | hip-hop | ambient | gospel | metal  |
| Color           | turquise     | grey     | amber  | red   | yellow    |
| Job         | manager | fisherman    | writer | designer  | nurse |

