.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-2::.
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: davidoff, alhambra, game, havana, dunhill
House: gothic-revival, cottage, craftsman, cape-cod, tower
City: boston, liverpool, london, rome, marseilles
5 different games are played: snooker, bridge, domino, chess, canasta
 1. the cape-cod house is on the right of the person playing snooker##1
 2. the person playing domino is the person traveling to liverpool##1
 3. the person playing bridge is on the right of the person playing chess##1
 4. the person traveling to london is on the far left##1
 5. the person traveling to marseilles is on the right of the person traveling to rome##1
 6. the craftsman house is on the right of the person traveling to london##1
 7. the tower house is on the left of the person traveling to boston##1
 8. the game-smoker is the person traveling to london##1
 9. the person playing chess is the game-smoker##1
10. the alhambra-smoker is in the middle##1
11. the havana-smoker is on the left of the person playing domino##1
12. the game-smoker is the cottage house##1
13. the dunhill-smoker is on the left of the person playing snooker##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |      3       |      4       |     5      |
| Cigar          | game        | dunhill | alhambra     | havana      | davidoff  |
| House           | cottage   | craftsman | tower    | cape-cod | gothic-revival |
| City   | london | rome     | marseilles | boston    | liverpool  |
| Game   | chess     | bridge | snooker    | canasta      | domino    |

