.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-3::.
5 different pets are kept: mouse, rabbit, dog, chinchilla, horse
5 different games are played: chess, backgammon, go, monopoly, snooker
There 5 different types of food: garlic, cauliflower, pear, asparagus, banana
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: daffodil, daisy, begonia, sunflower, tulip
 1. the person playing monopoly is on the right of the person eating banana##1
 2. the person playing chess is on the right of the person playing go##1
 3. the person eating garlic is in the middle##1
 4. the owner of the rabbit is in the middle##1
 5. the person eating pear is on the far right##1
 6. the person playing backgammon is on the far left##1
 7. the person who growssunflower is on the right of the person who growsdaisy##1
 8. the person eating pear is on the right of the person eating asparagus##1
 9. the person who growstulip is in the middle##1
10. the person who growsbegonia is on the right of the person eating cauliflower##1
11. the person eating pear is the person playing chess##1
12. the owner of the horse is on the right of the owner of the mouse##1
13. the owner of the chinchilla is the person eating cauliflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |    2    |     3      |     4     |     5      |
| Pet      | chinchilla          | dog  | rabbit       | mouse     | horse      |
| Game         | backgammon | snooker | monopoly  | go   | chess    |
| Food   | cauliflower        | banana | garlic | asparagus    | pear   |
| Flower     | daffodil   | begonia | tulip      | daisy | sunflower |

