.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-4::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: handball, lacrosse, tennis, ice-hockey, basketball
5 different brands of cigars are smoked: chaman, montecristo, bongani, tiparillo, dunhill
5 different pets are kept: frog, lizard, ferret, fish, mouse
5 different games are played: monopoly, mah-jongg, billiard, poker, snooker
 1. the montecristo-smoker is on the left of the owner of the frog##1
 2. the chaman-smoker is on the right of the person who's sport is tennis##1
 3. the owner of the lizard is the montecristo-smoker##1
 4. the owner of the frog is the chaman-smoker##1
 5. the bongani-smoker is on the right of the owner of the fish##1
 6. the person playing billiard is on the right of the chaman-smoker##1
 7. the person playing mah-jongg is on the right of the dunhill-smoker##1
 8. the person playing snooker is in the middle##1
 9. the owner of the fish is on the left of the person who's sport is handball##1
10. the person who's sport is basketball is the owner of the ferret##1
11. the person who's sport is lacrosse is on the left of the person who's sport is basketball##1
12. the person playing monopoly is on the left of the owner of the mouse##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1      |     2      |   3    |    4    |     5     |
| Sport          | ice-hockey        | handball       | tennis | lacrosse   | basketball  |
| Cigar   | dunhill | bongani | montecristo | chaman   | tiparillo |
| Pet   | fish         | mouse     | lizard | frog | ferret     |
| Game     | monopoly        | mah-jongg        | snooker    | poker    | billiard      |

