5 different games are played: canasta, go, domino, billiard, chess
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: spy, western, animation, martial-arts, romance
House: townhouse, farmhouse, palace, cottage, tower
 1. the person watching western movies is the palace house##1
 2. the palace house is the person playing domino##1
 3. the person playing chess is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
 4. the person driving the ship is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 5. the tower house is on the right of the person driving the motorbike##1
 6. the person playing canasta is the townhouse house##1
 7. the person watching spy movies is on the right of the person playing billiard##1
 8. the person watching romance movies is in the middle##1
 9. the person driving the skateboard is on the left of the person watching western movies##1
10. the person driving the ship is on the far right##1
11. the person driving the trike is on the right of the person watching animation movies##1
12. the cottage house is on the left of the person driving the ship##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1        |    2     |     3     |      4       |      5      |
| Transport          | skateboard    | trike  | quad-bike | motorbike    | ship      |
| Game           | chess | domino | canasta  | billiard | go |
| Movie-Genre   | animation           | western      | romance      | martial-arts        | spy     |
| House         | farmhouse         | palace  | townhouse   | cottage       | tower  |

