There are 5 different favourite beverages: coffee, cola, sprite, fanta, almond-milk
There 5 different types of food: corn, watermelon, asparagus, grapes, apricot
 1. the person traveling to prague is the person eating apricot##1
 2. the person traveling to venice is on the right of the person drinking cola##1
 3. the person drinking coffee is on the far right##1
 4. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person driving the bus##1
 5. the person eating grapes is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 6. the person traveling to berlin is on the left of the person eating corn##1
 7. the person traveling to edinburgh is the person eating asparagus##1
 8. the person eating grapes is the person drinking fanta##1
 9. the person driving the quad-bike is on the far left##1
10. the person traveling to edinburgh is on the left of the person drinking almond-milk##1
11. the person driving the car is in the middle##1
12. the person eating grapes is the person driving the subway##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |    2     |     3      |     4     |       5       |
| Transport         | quad-bike  | subway  | car    | bus | trike |
| City   | prague        | venice  | edinburgh | berlin      | miami        |
| Beverage   | cola       | fanta  | sprite   | almond-milk | coffee     |
| Food         | apricot | grapes | asparagus | watermelon  | corn      |

