.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-17::.
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: orchid, bellflower, marigold, amaryllis, poppy
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: biathlon, surfing, climbing, skateboarding, sailing
There 5 different types of food: pineapple, asparagus, lettuce, lemon, spinach
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: february, october, september, august, december
 1. the person who's sport is surfing is on the left of the person eating spinach##1
 2. the person who growsorchid is on the far left##1
 3. the person who's sport is skateboarding is on the left of the person eating pineapple##1
 4. the person who's birthday is in october is on the left of the person eating asparagus##1
 5. the person who's sport is biathlon is on the left of the person who's birthday is in december##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in september is on the right of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 7. the person who's sport is surfing is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person eating pineapple is on the left of the person who's sport is biathlon##1
 9. the person who's birthday is in december is on the right of the person who growsamaryllis##1
10. the person who growspoppy is on the right of the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's sport is sailing##1
12. the person who's sport is climbing is the person eating lemon##1
13. the person who's sport is sailing is on the far right##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |     2      |      3       |   4    |    5     |
| Flower      | orchid      | bellflower       | poppy         | amaryllis  | marigold |
| Sport   | climbing  | skateboarding | surfing | biathlon  | sailing  |
| Food   | lemon    | asparagus    | pineapple        | spinach | lettuce     |
| Birthday           | october | september      | february       | august   | december   |

