.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-18::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, card-games, collecting, camping, traveling
The people grow 5 different varities of flowers: tulip, rose, azalea, orchid, bellflower
5 different games are played: domino, chess, canasta, snooker, poker
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: may, august, march, october, april
 1. the person playing snooker is on the right of the person playing poker##1
 2. the person who growsazalea is on the right of the person who's birthday is in april##1
 3. the person playing canasta is on the left of the person who's birthday is in october##1
 4. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##1
 5. the person playing poker is on the left of the person who growsazalea##1
 6. the person who's birthday is in august is on the left of the person who's hobby is traveling##1
 7. the person who's hobby is card-games is the person who's birthday is in may##1
 8. the person who's hobby is collecting is the person who growsrose##1
 9. the person playing chess is in the middle##1
10. the person playing domino is the person who growsbellflower##1
11. the person who's birthday is in october is on the right of the person who growsorchid##1
12. the person who's hobby is traveling is on the left of the person playing snooker##1
13. the person who's hobby is camping is the person who growsbellflower##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |    2     |    3    |     4      |     5     |
| Hobby   | card-games      | camping | collecting  | traveling    | drawing |
| Flower   | orchid     | bellflower     | rose | tulip      | azalea      |
| Game           | canasta       | domino     | chess     | poker     | snooker   |
| Birthday         | may | october | august  | april | march   |

