.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-19::.
The people prefer 5 different types of sport: basketball, badminton, climbing, soccer, biathlon
There are 5 different favourite colors: apricot, emerald, blue, yellow, aquamarine
The people have 5 different hobbies: drawing, sudoku, singing, board-games, dancing
The people perfer 5 different movie-genres: family, epic, documentary, fantasy, comedy
 1. the person who's hobby is sudoku is on the left of the person who's hobby is board-games##1
 2. the person watching comedy movies is on the right of the person watching epic movies##1
 3. the person who likes aquamarine is the person watching family movies##1
 4. the person watching documentary movies is on the far right##1
 5. the person watching epic movies is the person who's sport is climbing##1
 6. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person who's hobby is singing##1
 7. the person who's sport is soccer is on the left of the person who likes emerald##1
 8. the person watching comedy movies is on the left of the person watching family movies##1
 9. the person watching family movies is in the middle##1
10. the person who's hobby is dancing is on the right of the person who's hobby is singing##1
11. the person who likes apricot is on the left of the person watching comedy movies##1
12. the person who likes blue is the person who's sport is biathlon##1
13. the person who's hobby is board-games is on the left of the person who's sport is badminton##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |    1     |   2    |   3    |   4    |   5    |
| Sport      | climbing | biathlon    | badminton   | soccer   | basketball |
| Color   | apricot    | blue   | aquamarine | yellow | emerald  |
