.:: Puzzle 4x5-Level-1-20::.
The people have 5 different hobbies: dancing, photography, writing, woodworking, card-games
5 different pets are kept: cat, horse, snake, dog, lizard
The people's birthday is in 5 different months: september, february, august, may, december
There are 5 different favourite colors: ivory, amber, fuchsia, apricot, ebony
 1. the person who's hobby is writing is in the middle##1
 2. the owner of the dog is the person who likes ivory##1
 3. the person who's hobby is writing is on the left of the owner of the dog##1
 4. the owner of the cat is the person who's birthday is in december##1
 5. the person who likes ebony is on the far right##1
 6. the person who likes apricot is on the right of the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
 7. the owner of the snake is the person who's birthday is in february##1
 8. the person who likes amber is on the right of the person who's hobby is photography##1
 9. the person who likes ebony is on the right of the person who's hobby is dancing##1
10. the person who's hobby is photography is on the far left##1
11. the owner of the cat is on the far right##1
12. the owner of the lizard is in the middle##1
13. the person who's birthday is in september is the person who's hobby is woodworking##1
14. the person who's birthday is in may is on the left of the person who likes ebony##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |       1       |     2     |    3    |     4      |   5    |
| Hobby      | photography | woodworking   | writing    | dancing       | card-games |
| Pet   | snake           | horse   | lizard   | dog       | cat  |
| Birthday   | february       | september | august | may     | december   |
| Color     | fuchsia    | amber   | apricot   | ivory | ebony   |

 